metadata.description:
RETURNLABEL // you already know -- one of many 

--- 
Written / Recorded by Domino 
Produced by Testagrossa 
Mixed / Mastered by Steeziak

lyrics.text:
Aye its mr unforgetten 
Mr unforgettable 
They call me mr love 
Im feeling so incredible 
The instrumental makes It obvious 
Had to throw in on a grill for my cocky shit 
Hit jay just to bring the diamonds before stones event 
Then we hit the stones event 
On some collaboration 
Aint a rolling stone but Ill roll into vacations 
Stoned 
Smoking j’s up on my throne 
Hit my telly telly telly phone 
And ill text you from my celly 
Baked dough to give cuts to all my friends like a deli 
Still singing like Adele 
Connected like a dell 
Saw copperfield and started wishing up some spells 
For the hell of Itttt
Tell me what’s your purpose 
I cant barely feel your fire burning at the surface … 
Some might need a quick change to juggle off this circus 
No circuits connected where’s the spark or the furnace ? 
Tryna feel the heat... tryna get you off your feet, out the street... out the pardon of your feet. 
What you mean? what you meaning what you mean? had to get It on my back just to park It for the keys
